                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-1 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13142.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13142.htm">成功無短路 [ SÊNG-KONG BÔ TÉ-LŌ͘ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">成功無短路
 　　「彼時耶穌予聖神chhōa到曠野，欲受魔鬼試。」　馬太4章1節。
　　欲造成品性，無有近&ecirc;路；&agrave;i得著近路&ecirc;，攏是做誘惑&ecirc;根源。亞當kap夏娃論in &ecirc;智慧&ecirc;發達是親像囡仔。對佇食果子，in想隨時&agrave;i欲得著彼个智慧。智慧是好&ecirc;物，猶久袂會佇一時陣來得著。智慧是親像一个媠&ecirc;記念塔，起佇忍耐、勞苦&ecirc;地基頂。亞當kap夏娃行短&ecirc;路&agrave;i欲得著智慧，反轉續陷落罪。
　　主&ecirc;受試猶原有相同&ecirc;教示佇teh。「人會...<a href="artical-13142.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
